{"tid":185694,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[請注意]LIHKG香港女神聯賽 賽會特別消息","createTime":"2017-04-03T15:55:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-02T10:52:47.000Z","uid":92376,"like":6,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"59c16f8d25f88e90331d1511ed97c0ec3e2986d9","tid":185694,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T15:55:52.000Z","msg":"由於本會自聯賽開季而嚟,一直都收到唔少巴打既意見<br />\n因為佢地成日留意唔到賽事投選專區既post而白白錯過左投票既機會<br />\n呢方面我都覺得非常可惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而近日我地又發現推post技術上有一個困難<br />\n就係自推得太多,係會推唔返個post上黎<br />\n而呢點亦都求證過LIHKG管理員確定係有件咁既怪事<br />\n雖然其他巴打可以幫手,但始終會好影響活動既推廣<br />\n<br />\n再加上來季賽會將會增設本地盃賽及環球冠軍盃等賽事<br />\n有見及此,為左更方便一眾巴打得知投票或提名消息<br />\n<strong>LIHKG女神聯賽比賽日及特別事項通知TG channel</strong>面世啦,我地會有專人喺賽事前,同進行緊既時候發佈投票事項通知,加入左既巴打就會收到通知,唔駛擔心miss左啦,TG channel保障用戶私隱,我同你同你,仲有你你你都唔會知道其他人既資訊,仲諗咩?即刻睇睇下面啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb6de10796fa399133f6e41f1354c231989c0122","tid":185694,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T15:58:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a983753887e7e17a9f658f86446ce5fc16e5dc32","tid":185694,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T16:09:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d05d9096c46a9a7ccdd49ee15b4bf617c54562fa","tid":185694,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T16:20:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57279ea76fc3e3f2